    `applied_discount_amount` DECIMAL(18,2) COMMENT 'The total discount amount applied to the new plan as part of this change. Includes promotional offers, retention discounts, and loyalty rewards. | Column applied_discount_amount (DECIMAL(15,2)) in subscriber.subscription_change',
    `applied_discount_percentage` DECIMAL(18,2) COMMENT 'The percentage discount applied to the new plan subscription fee. Used for promotion effectiveness analysis and revenue impact modeling. | Column applied_discount_percentage (DECIMAL(5,2)) in subscriber.subscription_change',
