    `mrr_impact_amount` DECIMAL(18,2) COMMENT 'The net change in monthly recurring revenue resulting from this subscription change. Positive for upgrades, negative for downgrades. Calculated as new_monthly_recurring_revenue minus previous_monthly_recurring_revenue. | Column mrr_impact_amount (DECIMAL(15,2)) in subscriber.subscription_change',
    `new_billing_period` STRING COMMENT 'The billing frequency of the new subscription plan. Enables analysis of billing period changes and their impact on cash flow and retention. | Column new_billing_period (STRING) in subscriber.subscription_change. Valid values are `monthly|quarterly|semi-annual|annual`',
    `new_monthly_recurring_revenue` DECIMAL(18,2) COMMENT 'The monthly recurring revenue amount from the new plan after this change. Used to calculate MRR expansion, contraction, and net revenue retention metrics. | Column new_monthly_recurring_revenue (DECIMAL(15,2)) in subscriber.subscription_change',
