    `proration_amount` DECIMAL(18,2) COMMENT 'The prorated credit or charge amount applied to the subscriber account due to mid-cycle plan changes. Positive values represent charges, negative values represent credits. | Column proration_amount (DECIMAL(15,2)) in subscriber.subscription_change',
