    `updated_timestamp` TIMESTAMP COMMENT 'Timestamp when the payment instrument record was last modified. Follows ISO 8601 format (yyyy-MM-ddTHH:mm:ss.SSSXXX). Used for audit trail and change tracking. | Column updated_timestamp (TIMESTAMP) in subscriber.payment_instrument',
    `verification_date` DATE COMMENT 'Date when the payment instrument was successfully verified. Used for compliance tracking and fraud prevention. | Column verification_date (DATE) in subscriber.payment_instrument',
    `verification_status` STRING COMMENT 'Status of payment instrument verification process. Indicates whether the payment method has been successfully validated through AVS, CVV check, or micro-deposit verification. | Column verification_status (STRING) in subscriber.payment_instrument. Valid values are `verified|unverified|failed|pending`',
