    `title_id` BIGINT COMMENT 'Foreign key linking to content.title. Business justification: Promotional offers often require viewing or purchasing specific titles (e.g., "watch premiere to unlock discount"). Supports campaign attribution, content-driven acquisition, and partnership promotion | Column qualifying_title_id (BIGINT) in content.offer_redemption',
