    `last_verified_timestamp` TIMESTAMP COMMENT 'The timestamp when the MVPD affiliation was last verified with the provider. Used to determine if re-authentication is required. | Column last_verified_timestamp (TIMESTAMP) in subscriber.mvpd_affiliation',
    `max_content_rating` STRING COMMENT 'The maximum content rating allowed under this MVPD affiliations parental controls. Content rated above this level is blocked. [ENUM-REF-CANDIDATE: G|PG|PG-13|R|NC-17|TV-Y|TV-Y7|TV-G|TV-PG|TV-14|TV-MA â€” 11 candidates stripped; promote to reference product] | Column max_content_rating (STRING) in subscriber.mvpd_affiliation',
