    `mvpd_type` STRING COMMENT 'Classification of the MVPD provider type: traditional MVPD (cable/satellite), virtual MVPD (streaming), telco (IPTV), or other distribution model. | Column mvpd_type (STRING) in subscriber.mvpd_affiliation. Valid values are `mvpd|vmvpd|telco|satellite|cable`',
